50|$|In 2000, Pan Africa Insurance Company Limited {{entered into}} a {{strategic}} partnership with African Life Assurance of South Africa. This was through an acquisition of a minority stake in Pan Africa Insurance Holdings Limited <b>by</b> <b>Hubris</b> Holdings Limited, African Life Assurance investment vehicle.|$|R
