50|$|Diseases of {{foxtail millet}} include leaf and head blast disease <b>caused</b> <b>by</b> Magnaporthe grisea, smut disease <b>caused</b> <b>by</b> Ustilago crameri, and green ear <b>caused</b> <b>by</b> Sclerospora graminicola. The unharvested crop is also {{susceptible}} to attack by birds and rodents.|$|R
